[Question] Who is Aaron Price related to?
[A] William Price and Joyce Price
[B] Chloe Price and William Price
[C] Joyce Price and Chloe Price
[D] William Price and Max Caulfield
[Answer] A

[Question] What does Aaron apologize for in his letter to William?
[A] Not being able to visit him
[B] Not sending him enough money
[C] Not being able to attend his wedding
[D] Not being able to help him with his car
[Answer] B

[Question] Where is Aaron being sent for work in the alternative timeline?
[A] Salt Lake City
[B] Los Angeles
[C] New York City
[D] San Francisco
[Answer] A

[Question] What does William thank Aaron for in his email?
[A] A pressure washer
[B] A car
[C] A lawnmower
[D] A bicycle
[Answer] A

[Question] What does William offer Aaron in his email?
[A] A cold beer
[B] A hot coffee
[C] A glass of wine
[D] A cup of tea
[Answer] A
